      "C"
    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>When 2-methylhexane is passed over $\\mathrm{Cr}_2 \\mathrm{O}_3$ at 773 K , toluene is formed as $A$.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2023 (Online) 13th May Morning Shift Chemistry - Carboxylic Acids and Its Derivatives Question 9 English Explanation 1\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6py6/23a70ef1-889a-473c-9f20-6a70a4682297/c9e25fe0-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6py7.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6py6/23a70ef1-889a-473c-9f20-6a70a4682297/c9e25fe0-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6py7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p>$A$ reacts with $\\mathrm{KMnO}_4 / \\mathrm{OH}^{-}$followed by acidic hydrolysis to give Bi.e. benzoic acid.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2023 (Online) 13th May Morning Shift Chemistry - Carboxylic Acids and Its Derivatives Question 9 English Explanation 2\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6r3x/1468024a-74c6-4e6f-8e64-c5b0a512edbb/cac7b6d0-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6r3y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6r3x/1468024a-74c6-4e6f-8e64-c5b0a512edbb/cac7b6d0-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6r3y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p>This benzoic acid undergoes nitration in presence of mixture of conc. $\\mathrm{H}_2 \\mathrm{SO}_4$ and conc. $\\mathrm{HNO}_3$ to give $m$-nitrobenzoic acid $(C)$.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2023 (Online) 13th May Morning Shift Chemistry - Carboxylic Acids and Its Derivatives Question 9 English Explanation 3\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6sci/6c072cd4-21ca-4b86-89c8-8c99c5e40af6/cbbc9e20-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6scj.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mkfg6sci/6c072cd4-21ca-4b86-89c8-8c99c5e40af6/cbbc9e20-f210-11f0-aa7a-bbc1e273ac26/file-jaoe38c1mkfg6scj.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>",
    "topic": null,
