    "content": "<p>The major product of the following reactions</p>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2022 (Online) 19th July Evening Shift Chemistry - Carboxylic Acids and Its Derivatives Question 2 English\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mnbw5bvq/4cd46d1d-4326-4fca-8033-48f9939bbfd9/b8d04060-2b80-11f1-9b76-91a623d95264/file-jaoe38c1mnbw5bvr.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mnbw5bvq/4cd46d1d-4326-4fca-8033-48f9939bbfd9/b8d04060-2b80-11f1-9b76-91a623d95264/file-jaoe38c1mnbw5bvr.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>",
